===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: qiú shēng bùdé, qiú sĭ bùnéng
===Idiom===
'''[[求]][[生]][[不得]]，[[求]][[死]][[不能]]'''
# can't live and you can't die; between a rock and a hard place; in a bind; in a pickle
